AI development is shifting to an important new phase, with AI agents that can pull fresh information from the web, plan, and execute tasks autonomously. These agents, instead of relying solely on their training data, can interact with the internet to find and make use of the latest data signals. This kind of dynamic exploration... Read more »

title: Letting AI agents navigate and interact with the web
